value.title: Pier 49
value.description:
About Event

​3-mile loop through the best parts of the Presidio! We’ll be hitting the "Big Three" highlights: the redwood forest, the bay views, and the Andy Goldsworthy art installations.

​It’s a moderate, chatty pace—mostly trails and quiet footpaths (no walking on busy roads). We'll get some fresh air, see some cool art, and enjoy the city views.

​Route (~2.6 miles):

​🌲 Up: We start on the Ecology Trail, winding up through the redwoods.

​📸 View: A quick stop at Inspiration Point for view
